type.description: The type of order, such as d2c, b2b, dropship, or transfer.

scac.description: The Standard Carrier Alpha Code for the carrier used to ship the order.

is_third_party_freight.description: True if the order was shipped using a third party freight account.

third_party_freight_account_number.description: The third party freight account number used to ship the order.

first_party_freight_account_number.description: The first party freight account number used to ship the order.

invoice_currency_code.description: The currency used for this order. If not provided explicitly, defaults to USD.

total_price.description: The total price a customer paid for the order.

total_tax.description: The total tax on the order.

total_discount.description: The total amount discounted from the order.

total_shipping.description: The total shipping cost for the order incurred by the customer.

line_items.description: List of the products included in the order.

tags.description: A list of tags associated with the order. Tags that are represented as key-value pairs in the WMS will be represented as a single string formatted as `key:value`.

items.description: A tag associated with the order.

required_ship_date.description: The date the order must be shipped by.

saturday_delivery.description: True if the order requires Saturday delivery.

signature_required.description: True if the order requires a signature upon delivery.

international_duty_paid_by.description: The party responsible for paying international duties.

shipments.description: List of the shipments sent out to the customer.

external_system_url.description: URL link to the order in the external system (WMS/Freight etc).
